Reference : https://github.com/in28minutes/SpringBootForBeginners

Introduction : This project is all about POC on spring Boot Just Basic.


************************ More Info ************************************

when setup this project in new machine. if any error related to maven
	- right click on project - > maven - > update project.


1) Annotation That Spring look for when it start.

   @Component @RestController @Controller @Service @Repository
   
2) Testing step for Spring Boot Project.
   
   * Right click on Application run as Java application.
   * This will start embeded tomcat server.
   * test url : http://localhost:8080/welcome
   
